      "card": {
        "eyebrow": "QUANTUM MECHANICS",
        "headline": "Echo at t = 2\u03c4.\nAmplitude: e^(\u22122\u03c4/T\u2082).",
        "dek": "The \u03c0-pulse exchanges fast and slow spins. Inhomogeneous dephasing is reversible; real T2 decay is not."
